'''艾莉森·克里斯汀·麦克'''（{{lang-en|Allison Christin Mack}}，又译'''爱莉森·麦克'''、'''艾莉森·马克'''，{{bd|1982年|7月29日|||Mack, Allison}}），美国女演员，因在《[[超人前传|超人前传]]》饰演克洛伊·苏利文（Chloe Sullivan）和在《[[犬友笑传|犬友笑传]]》中饰演阿曼达（Amanda）而为人所知。

在2018年，麥克因擔任[[NXIVM|NXIVM]]的其中一名高級成員而得到媒體注意，NXIVM是一個被指控從事勒索、性交易和強迫勞動的組織，為此它被一些專家指責為[[邪教|邪教]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://artvoice.com/2018/03/27/allison-mack-expected-arrested-next/#.Wt6b85criUl |title = Allison Mack expected to be arrested next |author = Chitra Selvaraj |date = 2018-03-27 |publisher = Artvoice |language = en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/news/nxivm-what-we-know-about-alleged-sex-trafficking-forced-labor-w518483 |title = NXIVM: What We Know About Alleged Sex Trafficking, Forced Labor |author = Laura Barcella |date = 2018-03-28 |publisher = Rolling Stone |language = en}}</ref>2018年4月20日，麥克因為性交易、共謀性交易和共謀強迫勞動的罪名而被[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]（FBI）逮捕。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/local/Actress-Allison-Mack-Arrested-Nxivm-Sex-Cult-480387783.html |title = 'Smallville' Actress Allison Mack Arrested in Connection to NXIVM Sex Cult Case |author =  Jonathan Dienst |date = 2018-04-23 |publisher = WNBC |language = en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-43846243 |title = Allison Mack, Smallville actress, charged over Nxivm sex trafficking |date = 2018-04-21 |publisher = BBC News |language = en}}</ref>麥克在2019年4月承認犯有敲詐勒索罪。2021年6月30日，麥克被判處入獄3年。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/allison-mack-sentenced-3-years-prison-nxivm-sex-cult-165358008.html |title = Allison Mack sentenced to 3 years in prison for role in NXIVM sex cult |author = Taryn Ryder |date = 2021-07-01 |language = en}}</ref>

== 早年 ==
艾莉森·麦克於1982年7月29日出生在[[西德|西德]]的[[普雷茨|普雷茨]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.fandango.com/people/allison-mack-414790/biography |title = Allison Mack Biography |publisher = Fandango |language = en |deadurl = bot: unknown |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180406213759/https://www.fandango.com/people/allison-mack-414790/biography |archivedate = 2018年4月6日 |df =  }}</ref><ref name=FilmReference>{{Cite web |url = http://www.filmreference.com/film/32/Allison-Mack.html |title = Allison Mack Biography (1982-) |publisher = Film Reference |language = en |deadurl = bot: unknown |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180406214922/http://www.filmreference.com/film/32/Allison-Mack.html |archivedate = 2018年4月6日 |df =  }}</ref>，是歌劇歌手乔纳森·麦克（Jonathan Mack）和明蒂·麦克（Mindy Mack）的女兒<ref name=FilmReference />，因為父母當時在德國表演所以生在德国，两岁时搬回[[加利福尼亚|加利福尼亚]]居住。她是三个孩子中的第二个，還有一名叫香农（Shannon）的哥哥和一個名叫萝宾（Robyn）的妹妹。

